OL,3,CFootball's youngest boss: 'My family
OL,4,Cstruggle with abuse'
OL,6,FFootball's youngest chief executive
OL,7,Fsays his family "struggles" with the
OL,8,Fabuse he has received since he took
OL,9,Fthe job.
OL,11,FRyan Sparks was just 29 when he was
OL,12,Fappointed boss of his hometown
OL,13,Ffootball club Bradford City, making
OL,14,Fhim the youngest CEO in the Football
OL,15,FLeague.
OL,17,FHe said: "I had a goal to get to a
OL,18,Fchief executive role by the time I was
OL,19,F30, and I achieved it at 29."
