OL,3,CFootball's youngest boss: 'My family
OL,4,Cstruggle with abuse'
OL,6,FBut being in charge of a one-time
OL,7,FPremier League club now languishing in
OL,8,FLeague Two has made him a target for
OL,9,Fthe ire of some disgruntled fans.
OL,11,F"You can imagine when I became chief
OL,12,Fexecutive that was met with a lot of
OL,13,Fcriticism. I understood that, but it
OL,14,Fwasn't nice for me and it wasn't nice
OL,15,Ffor my family.
OL,17,F"Sometimes some of the stuff I receive
OL,18,Fcan be quite hurtful. Not so much for
OL,19,Fme, but I know my family struggle with
OL,20,Fit.
