OL,15,FWith a degree in sports journalism
OL,16,Ffrom Huddersfield University, Sparks
OL,17,Fhad previously worked at rugby league
OL,18,Fclubs Bradford Bulls and Featherstone
OL,19,FRovers before becoming director of
OL,20,Fcommunications at Valley Parade.
