OL,6,FThree years later he was promoted to
OL,7,FCEO, his predecessor Julian Rhondes
OL,8,Fdescribing Sparks as "an experienced
OL,9,Foperator in professional sport"
OL,10,Fdespite his tender years.
OL,12,FHowever despite this glowing
OL,13,Ftestimonial Sparks felt his age was
OL,14,Foften an issue for some.
OL,16,F"I was seen as a cheap option," he
OL,17,Fsaid. "I was too young, out of my
OL,18,Fdepth. I'd never been a chief
OL,19,Fexecutive before. All those things
OL,20,Fdon't fill people with confidence."
