OL,6,FSparks says his age has not been "held
OL,7,Fagainst me" by people he works with
OL,8,Fbut he has not been "patronised" by
OL,9,Fpeople within the game and admits has
OL,10,Fmade mistakes in the four years since
OL,11,Fhis appointment.
OL,13,F'No regrets'
OL,15,FFormer Manchester United and Barcelona
OL,16,Fstriker Mark Hughes was a high profile
OL,17,Fchoice as manager two years ago.
