OL,6,FAlthough he steered the club to the
OL,7,FLeague Two playoffs in his only full
OL,8,Fseason in charge, Hughes was sacked
OL,9,Fafter a disappointing start to this
OL,10,Fseason.
OL,12,F"I've made plenty of poor decisions,
OL,13,Fnot for the wrong reasons. But
OL,14,Fdecisions that haven't worked out.
OL,15,FEqually there have been some good ones
OL,16,Fthat have taken the club forward.
OL,18,F"Hindsight is a wonderful thing, but I
OL,19,Fdon't have any regrets."
