OL,6,FGraham Alexander was Sparks' choice as
OL,7,FHughes' replacement and, despite an
OL,8,Fencouraging run of six straight wins
OL,9,Fat the end of 2023, Bradford have
OL,10,Fsince gone seven games without a
OL,11,Fleague victory.
OL,13,FThey sit 18th in League Two, a
OL,14,Fposition not good enough for many of
OL,15,Fthe 15,000 season ticket holders.
