OL,3,CFootball's youngest boss: 'My family
OL,4,Cstruggle with abuse'
OL,6,F"You're not going to be liked by
OL,7,Feveryone," Sparks said. "That's
OL,8,Fanother thing I very quickly had to
OL,9,Flearn. If you want to be popular,
OL,10,Fprobably don't do this job. I have
OL,11,Ftried to run this club from my heart."
OL,13,FSparks insists he still enjoys his job
OL,14,Fand says it's a privilege to represent
OL,15,Fhis hometown club.
OL,17,FAnd with Bradford just one more win
OL,18,Faway from a Wembley appearance in the
OL,19,FEFL Trophy, a difficult season could
OL,20,Fend with a memorable day for the club.
